overview:
Baynetwork has grown to be the premier provider of new, used, refurbished and pre-owned network hardware and computer equipment.

With savings of up to 80% off retail price with extraordinary support and warranty, offering top brands such as Juniper, HP, Dell, Cisco, Extreme, IXIA and Shoretel. Some of the hardware include switches, routers, firewalls, servers and a wide range of network hardware.

Baynetwork is the leading provider of new, used and refurbished computer and networking equipment. Baynetwork resell and provide computer and network equipment including Juniper, Cisco, HP, Dell, Shoretel, and many more. With U.S. offices in San Fransisco, California and Las Vegas, Nevada, Baynetwork is also complimented by satellite locations in Germany, UK, Hungary and Russia.

Baynetwork provides it’s customers industry’s best managed IT and MIS Services for computer infrastructure as well as Cisco buy back, Cisco repair, recycling and refurbishing services.
